<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Pago pendiente de validar</title>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f0f4f8; min-height: 100vh;">
    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color: #f0f4f8; padding: 32px 16px;">
        <tr>
            <td align="center">
                <table width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; max-width: 600px; box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(24,36,50,0.08);">

                    <!-- Header with logo -->
                    <tr>
                        <td style="background-color: #184373; padding: 28px 32px; text-align: center;">
                            <span style="color: #ffffff; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1px;">Vent<span style="color: #5ACAF0;">IA</span></span>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <!-- Icon + Title -->
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 40px 32px 24px; text-align: center;">
                            <table width="64" height="64" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" align="center" style="margin: 0 auto 20px;">
                                <tr>
                                    <td style="background-color: #C8ECFD; width: 64px; height: 64px; border-radius: 50%; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;">
                                        <span style="font-size: 28px;">&#128179;</span>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>
                            <h1 style="margin: 0 0 8px 0; color: #182432; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.3px;">
                                Pago pendiente de validar
                            </h1>
                            <p style="margin: 0; color: #6b7280; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5;">
                                Un cliente envió un comprobante de pago
                            </p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <!-- Info card -->
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 0 32px 28px;">
                            <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color: #C8ECFD; border-radius: 10px; border-left: 4px solid #5ACAF0;">
                                <tr>
                                    <td style="padding: 20px 24px;">
                                        <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                                            <tr>
                                                <td style="padding-bottom: 14px;">
                                                    <p style="margin: 0 0 2px 0; color: #184373; font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.8px; font-weight: 600;">Cliente</p>
                                                    <p style="margin: 0; color: #182432; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600;"><%= @contact_name %></p>
                                                </td>
                                            </tr>
                                            <tr>
                                                <td>
                                                    <p style="margin: 0 0 2px 0; color: #184373; font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.8px; font-weight: 600;">Cuenta</p>
                                                    <p style="margin: 0; color: #182432; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600;"><%= @account_name %></p>
                                                </td>
                                            </tr>
                                        </table>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <!-- CTA Button -->
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 0 32px 36px; text-align: center;">
                            <a href="<%= @conversation_url %>" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #2F7CF4; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px; padding: 14px 36px; border-radius: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.2px;">
                                Revisar pago
                            </a>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <!-- Footer -->
                    <tr>
                        <td style="background-color: #182432; padding: 24px 32px;">
                            <p style="margin: 0 0 6px 0; font-size: 12px; color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.6; text-align: center;">
                                Recibiste este email porque tienes activadas las notificaciones de pagos pendientes en VentIA.
                            </p>
                            <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 11px; color: #64748b; text-align: center;">
                                &copy; 2026 VentIA. Todos los derechos reservados.
                            </p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                </table>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>
